        ### Boggle Game ###
        
press "Run" on the "boggle.py" file.
find words and get points!

1) The game has 3 pages: Welcome Screen,
 Game Screen and Finish Screen.
2) While playing the user can chose whichever
 word buttons he likes, than the pressed buttons
 change their background color.
3) When moving the mouse over a word button
 the button change his background color.
4) The user can click on the Delete button to
erase the last button he pressed, he can do it until all the
 pressed buttons are erased. The colors are changed accordingly.
5) When the 3 minutes is over the score of the last game
 will be shown with the highest score of the last games.
